      "title": "The odd couple: Margaret Archer, Anthony Giddens and British social theory",
      "authors": [
        {
          "name": "Anthony King",
          "openalex_id": "A5008930821",
          "orcid": "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7735-7014",
